ct-rive-present-tab" style="display:none" class="fig-xi606m"><p class="fig-1fgkanl">Prompt to code anything you can imagine with AI.</p><a class="fig-1ehzf5h" href="https://www.figma.com/make/"><span class="btn-inner fig-1qhfzz9"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="btn-builtin-icon fig-1kjx4xt"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.522 4.25 20 12l-7.478 7.75-.733-.709 6.302-6.531H4v-1.02h14.09L11.79 4.959z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg><span class="btn-text fig-87d5u0">Explore Figma Make</span></span></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="fig-11tqvy7"><div class="fig-2qv4k"><figure class="fig-mxb2ew"><div><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="64" height="56" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 64 56" aria-hidden="true" class="fig-1eiqq1"><g fill="currentColor"><path d="M29.866 0v24.286H14.79V26h.143c8.246 0 14.93 6.715 14.93 15 0 8.283-6.684 14.999-14.93 14.999C6.685 56 0 49.284 0 41q0-.215.006-.428H0V17.143C0 7.675 7.64 0 17.064 0zM64 0v24.286H48.923V26h.142c8.247 0 14.931 6.715 14.931 15 0 8.283-6.684 14.999-14.93 14.999-8.247 0-14.932-6.716-14.932-15q0-.215.006-.428h-.006V17.143C34.134 7.675 41.774 0 51.198 0z"></path></g></svg><blockquote class="fig-1dbhnvn"><div class="fig-1mrohuj"><p>Figma helps us paint the north star for the whole company. It keeps everyone aligned and excited.</p></div></blockquote></div><figcaption class="fig-k4udfn"><img class="fig-1vtux4v" width="171" height="48" alt="Perplexity logo" src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/de3717bbf05134da0b92f1104c1027228e998fae-171x48.svg?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format"/><div class="fig-rvp98e"><div class="fig-sd3eu1"><div class="fig-5xfutw"></div><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="" class="fig-tm5os0" width="48" height="48" data-lqip="true"/><img data-loading="true" class="fig-134uger" width="48" height="48" loading="lazy" alt="" src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/4b1d8b9d27cbb85f931c4a67cbdd7abad42e06bc-600x600.png?w=48&amp;h=48&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format" srcSet="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/4b1d8b9d27cbb85f931c4a67cbdd7abad42e06bc-600x600.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.5 24w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/4b1d8b9d27cbb85f931c4a67cbdd7abad42e06bc-600x600.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.75 36w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/4b1d8b9d27cbb85f931c4a67cbdd7abad42e06bc-600x600.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format 48w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/4b1d8b9d27cbb85f931c4a67cbdd7abad42e06bc-600x600.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=1.5 72w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/4b1d8b9d27cbb85f931c4a67cbdd7abad42e06bc-600x600.png?w=48&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=2 96w"/></div><div><p class="fig-jljp6g"><span class="fig-13o7eu2">Henry Modisett</span><span class="fig-13o7eu2">Head of Design</span></p></div></div></figcaption></figure></div></section><section class="fig-6y04jb"><div class="fig-92lpi3"><div class="fig-7looi"><h2 class="fig-87ew1r">Bring everyone together with systems that scale</h2></div><section class="fig-gcn2ga"><div class="fig-z0kf9t"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="A UI design interface showing card components for a travel app. The left side displays icon sets and two card templates: a &quot;Card/Travel&quot; component showing a JFK flight (13:10p → 11:5, non-stop, Round trip $12) and a &quot;Card/Activity&quot; component below it. The right sidebar shows a color library with various background and text color options including dark, light, lime, gold, and neon variants." class="fig-vgi589" data-lqip="true"/><img data-loading="true" class="fig-c1ojco" loading="lazy" alt="A UI design interface showing card components for a travel app. The left side displays icon sets and two card templates: a &quot;Card/Travel&quot; component showing a JFK flight (13:10p → 11:5, non-stop, Round trip $12) and a &quot;Card/Activity&quot; component below it. The right sidebar shows a color library with various background and text color options including dark, light, lime, gold, and neon variants." src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/2f1c0ba703010a1b4126b14a9b0a65695e2655c2-1260x944.png?w=1260&amp;h=944&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format" srcSet="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/2f1c0ba703010a1b4126b14a9b0a65695e2655c2-1260x944.png?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.5 630w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/2f1c0ba703010a1b4126b14a9b0a65695e2655c2-1260x944.png?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.75 945w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/2f1c0ba703010a1b4126b14a9b0a65695e2655c2-1260x944.png?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=2 1260w"/><div class="fig-0"><h3 class="fig-7hfnf0">Share libraries and design systems across teams.</h3> <p class="fig-1ibk0rt">Create reusable components, variables, and brand assets to keep your entire organization building with the same visual language.</p></div><a class="fig-1xo1nb2" href="https://www.figma.com/design-systems/"><span class="btn-inner fig-1qhfzz9"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="btn-builtin-icon fig-1kjx4xt"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.522 4.25 20 12l-7.478 7.75-.733-.709 6.302-6.531H4v-1.02h14.09L11.79 4.959z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg><span class="btn-text fig-87d5u0">Explore design systems</span></span></a></div><div class="fig-z0kf9t"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Multiple assets surrounding button to &quot;Export assets&quot;" class="fig-vgi589" data-lqip="true"/><img data-loading="true" class="fig-c1ojco" loading="lazy" alt="Multiple assets surrounding button to &quot;Export assets&quot;" src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/d2d61daa22d944ec3cd62677c2adf8394496f903-1260x944.png?w=1260&amp;h=944&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format" srcSet="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/d2d61daa22d944ec3cd62677c2adf8394496f903-1260x944.png?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.5 630w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/d2d61daa22d944ec3cd62677c2adf8394496f903-1260x944.png?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.75 945w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/d2d61daa22d944ec3cd62677c2adf8394496f903-1260x944.png?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=2 1260w"/><div class="fig-0"><h3 class="fig-7hfnf0">Unlock your team with on-brand templates.</h3> <p class="fig-1ibk0rt">Share templates with your organization so anyone can quickly create social media assets, display ads, one-pagers, and more.</p></div><a class="fig-1xo1nb2" href="https://www.figma.com/buzz/"><span class="btn-inner fig-1qhfzz9"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="btn-builtin-icon fig-1kjx4xt"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.522 4.25 20 12l-7.478 7.75-.733-.709 6.302-6.531H4v-1.02h14.09L11.79 4.959z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg><span class="btn-text fig-87d5u0">Explore Figma Buzz</span></span></a></div><div class="fig-1qkml7u"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Screenshot of a web design interface showing a museum website with artwork displays on the left and a CSS development panel on the right. Pink cursors labeled &quot;Rico&quot; and &quot;Jane&quot; indicate multiple users collaborating on the design." class="fig-vekl8e" data-lqip="true"/><img data-loading="true" class="fig-i50dnj" loading="lazy" alt="Screenshot of a web design interface showing a museum website with artwork displays on the left and a CSS development panel on the right. Pink cursors labeled &quot;Rico&quot; and &quot;Jane&quot; indicate multiple users collaborating on the design." src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/278b3fae156f139de38afab1b0117410996a5f0e-2100x1183.png?w=2100&amp;h=1183&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format" srcSet="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/278b3fae156f139de38afab1b0117410996a5f0e-2100x1183.png?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.5 1050w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/278b3fae156f139de38afab1b0117410996a5f0e-2100x1183.png?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.75 1575w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/278b3fae156f139de38afab1b0117410996a5f0e-2100x1183.png?q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=2 2100w"/><div class="fig-0"><h3 class="fig-7hfnf0">Create one source of truth for devs and designers.</h3> <p class="fig-1ibk0rt">Get specs, annotations, and code snippets in one dedicated space with Dev Mode.</p></div><a class="fig-1xo1nb2" href="https://www.figma.com/dev-mode/"><span class="btn-inner fig-1qhfzz9"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="btn-builtin-icon fig-1kjx4xt"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.522 4.25 20 12l-7.478 7.75-.733-.709 6.302-6.531H4v-1.02h14.09L11.79 4.959z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg><span class="btn-text fig-87d5u0">Explore Dev Mode</span></span></a></div></section></div></section><section class="fig-1hysvv2"><div class="fig-1whjtwy"><div class="fig-aov7k0"><h2 class="fig-87ew1r">Ship products, any way you want</h2></div><div class="fig-42qb0p"><div class="fig-1yxd7ui"><div class="fig-gvtxu4"><h3 class="fig-11wp5ad"><button type="button" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="drawer-content-_R_36l9klubsodqivb_" id="drawer-title-_R_36l9klubsodqivb_" class="fig-bwla62"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="fig-1fyckd0"><g clip-path="url(#a)"><path fill="currentColor" d="M15.2 20.8v-1.075l.76.76a3.2 3.2 0 1 0 4.525-4.525l-.76-.76H20.8a3.2 3.2 0 0 0 0-6.4h-1.075l.76-.76a3.2 3.2 0 1 0-4.525-4.525l-.76.76V3.2a3.2 3.2 0 0 0-6.4 0v1.075l-.76-.76A3.2 3.2 0 1 0 3.515 8.04l.76.76H3.2a3.2 3.2 0 0 0 0 6.4h1.075l-.76.76a3.2 3.2 0 0 0 4.525 4.525l.76-.76V20.8a3.2 3.2 0 0 0 6.4 0"></path></g><defs><clipPath id="a"><path fill="#fff" d="M0 24h24V0H0z"></path></clipPath></defs></svg><span class="fig-2gtcnh">Turn Figma context into code</span></button></h3><div id="drawer-content-_R_36l9klubsodqivb_" role="region" aria-labelledby="drawer-title-_R_36l9klubsodqivb_" class="fig-w43dqe" style="opacity:0;height:0px"><p class="fig-w732xd">Our Figma MCP server lets you bring Figma context directly into your agentic coding tools.</p><a class="fig-1lctigx" href="https://www.figma.com/dev-mode/"><span class="btn-inner fig-1qhfzz9"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="btn-builtin-icon fig-1kjx4xt"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.522 4.25 20 12l-7.478 7.75-.733-.709 6.302-6.531H4v-1.02h14.09L11.79 4.959z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg><span class="btn-text fig-87d5u0">Explore Figma MCP</span></span></a><div class="fig-1o2fbcf"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Screenshot of a design-to-code interface showing completed API calls on the left and a user profile page for Julia Simmons on the right, displaying her location, membership details, and recent research activity." class="fig-j94shh" width="908" height="726" data-lqip="true"/><img data-loading="true" class="fig-do8qkc" sizes="calc(100vw - 24px), (min-width: 560px) 736px, (min-width: 960px) 720px, (min-width: 1920px) 908px" width="908" height="726" loading="eager" alt="Screenshot of a design-to-code interface showing completed API calls on the left and a user profile page for Julia Simmons on the right, displaying her location, membership details, and recent research activity." src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/24e122cd8a5089bd145f3fd46a35554bae2780b4-1560x1248.png?rect=0,1,1560,1247&amp;w=908&amp;h=726&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format" srcSet="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/24e122cd8a5089bd145f3fd46a35554bae2780b4-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.5 454w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/24e122cd8a5089bd145f3fd46a35554bae2780b4-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.75 681w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/24e122cd8a5089bd145f3fd46a35554bae2780b4-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format 908w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/24e122cd8a5089bd145f3fd46a35554bae2780b4-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=1.5 1362w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/24e122cd8a5089bd145f3fd46a35554bae2780b4-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=2 1560w"/></div></div></div><div class="fig-10y8asf"><h3 class="fig-11wp5ad"><button type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="drawer-content-_R_56l9klubsodqivb_" id="drawer-title-_R_56l9klubsodqivb_" class="fig-bwla62"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="fig-185q1t3"><path fill="currentColor" d="M22.4 24H1.6V8.8H6A.4.4 0 0 0 6 8h-.4a4 4 0 1 1 0-8h12.8a4 4 0 0 1 0 8H18a.4.4 0 0 0 0 .8h4.4z"></path></svg><span class="fig-1viykop">Publish custom websites—with or without code</span></button></h3><div hidden="" id="drawer-content-_R_56l9klubsodqivb_" role="region" aria-labelledby="drawer-title-_R_56l9klubsodqivb_" class="fig-w43dqe" style="opacity:0;height:0px"><p class="fig-w732xd">Design responsive websites in Figma Sites, then tweak with code or AI until everything is just right.</p><a class="fig-1lctigx" href="https://www.figma.com/sites/"><span class="btn-inner fig-1qhfzz9"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="btn-builtin-icon fig-1kjx4xt"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.522 4.25 20 12l-7.478 7.75-.733-.709 6.302-6.531H4v-1.02h14.09L11.79 4.959z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg><span class="btn-text fig-87d5u0">Explore Figma Sites</span></span></a><div class="fig-1o2fbcf"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Screenshot of a web design tool showing the Collectiv Gallery website interface with navigation sidebar on left and homepage preview featuring gallery description and artistic background image on right." class="fig-j94shh" width="908" height="726" data-lqip="true"/><img data-loading="true" class="fig-do8qkc" sizes="calc(100vw - 24px), (min-width: 560px) 736px, (min-width: 960px) 720px, (min-width: 1920px) 908px" width="908" height="726" loading="eager" alt="Screenshot of a web design tool showing the Collectiv Gallery website interface with navigation sidebar on left and homepage preview featuring gallery description and artistic background image on right." src="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/969d0fb681b2dfa08c6028611ded150d6df5595e-1560x1248.png?rect=0,1,1560,1247&amp;w=908&amp;h=726&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format" srcSet="https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/969d0fb681b2dfa08c6028611ded150d6df5595e-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.5 454w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/969d0fb681b2dfa08c6028611ded150d6df5595e-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=0.75 681w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/969d0fb681b2dfa08c6028611ded150d6df5595e-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format 908w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/969d0fb681b2dfa08c6028611ded150d6df5595e-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=1.5 1362w, https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/969d0fb681b2dfa08c6028611ded150d6df5595e-1560x1248.png?w=908&amp;q=75&amp;fit=max&amp;auto=format&amp;dpr=2 1560w"/></div></div></div><div class="fig-10y8asf"><h3 class="fig-11wp5ad"><button type="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="drawer-content-_R_76l9klubsodqivb_" id="drawer-title-_R_76l9klubsodqivb_" class="fig-bwla62"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="fig-19vjwa8"><g clip-path="url(#a)"><path fill="currentColor" d="M11.937 20.21 9.749 24H4.44a4.44 4.44 0 0 1-2.312-8.231A4.4 4.4 0 0 1 0 12c0-1.599.853-2.998 2.128-3.769A4.44 4.44 0 0 1 4.44 0h5.164l2.333 4.04L14.27 0h5.29a4.44 4.44 0 0 1 2.312 8.231A4.4 4.4 0 0 1 24 12a4.4 4.4 0 0 1-2.128 3.769A4.44 4.44 0 0 1 19.56 24h-5.435z"></path></g><defs><clipPath id="a"><path fill="#fff" d="M0 24h24V0H0z"></path></clipPath></defs></svg><span class="fig-1viykop">Ship products faster with AI</span></button></h3><div hidden="" id="drawer-content-_R_76l9klubsodqivb_" role="region" aria-labelledby="drawer-title-_R_76l9klubsodqivb_" class="fig-w43dqe" style="opacity:0;height:0px"><p class="fig-w732xd">Drop a design file into Figma Make and chat with AI to quickly create a live, functional app. </p><a class="fig-1lctigx" href="https://www.figma.com/make/"><span class="btn-inner fig-1qhfzz9"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true" class="btn-builtin-icon fig-1kjx4xt"><path fill="currentColor" fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.522 4.25 20 12l-7.478 7.75-.733-.709 6.302-6.531H4v-1.02h14.09L11.79 4.959z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg><span class="btn-text fig-87d5u0">Explore Figma Make</span></span></a><div class="fig-1o2fbcf"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Screenshot showing two card designs - a colorful tarot-style illustration and a &quot;Moon in Libra&quot; card with purple smiley face. Text requests creating a card-flip interaction between the designs, with a &quot;Thinking...&quot; 