ng world clock information against a vibrant rainbow gradient background. The top widget shows \\\"72°\\\" in dotted text with the current time \\\"12:43 PM\\\" in Atlanta, GA on Tuesday, Oct 10. Below is a \\\"LOCATIONS\\\" section listing times across different cities: New York (12:43 PM), Los Angeles (9:43 AM), Mexico City (11:43 AM), London (5:43 PM), and Paris (6:43 PM), each showing their time zone differences.\",\"href\":null,\"type\":\"informative\"}}}},{\"_key\":\"c526d1df8dc690d99ae49f98885b5ba8\",\"prompt\":\"Make text move on a path\",\"media\":{\"_type\":\"media\",\"mode\":\"embed\",\"embed\":{\"src\":\"https://vimeo.com/1103862294/802500bb17?share=copy\",\"ratio\":0.75,\"poster\":{\"_key\":null,\"_type\":\"contentImage\",\"asset\":{\"_id\":\"image-6e33dde58aba54986bef77ea81594b3c469daa86-842x1122-png\",\"_type\":\"sanity.imageAsset\",\"_rev\":\"xAzpLrs6BNV71CcUPamlEL\",\"extension\":\"png\",\"mimeType\":\"image/png\",\"originalFilename\":\"make-text-move-path.png\",\"path\":\"images/599r6htc/regionalized/6e33dde58aba54986bef77ea81594b3c469daa86-842x1122.png\",\"sha1hash\":\"6e33dde58aba54986bef77ea81594b3c469daa86\",\"size\":474683,\"url\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/images/599r6htc/regionalized/6e33dde58aba54986bef77ea81594b3c469daa86-842x1122.png\",\"_updatedAt\":\"2025-07-23T20:29:51Z\",\"metadata\":{\"dimensions\":{\"_type\":\"sanity.imageDimensions\",\"aspectRatio\":0.750445632798574,\"height\":1122,\"width\":842},\"lqip\":\"$2f\"}},\"crop\":null,\"hotspot\":null,\"alt\":\"A website for a dance studio called \\\"Rhythm Dance\\\" featuring a navigation menu (Home, Classes, About) and three main sections. The page displays black and white photographs decorated with bright green star and burst graphics: silhouettes of three dancers in poses under \\\"Our Curriculum,\\\" a close-up portrait of a woman with flowing hair under \\\"Our Instructors,\\\" and a group performance scene under \\\"2025 Community Showcase.\\\" The decorative green elements create a playful, energetic design overlay on the monochrome images.\",\"href\":null,\"type\":\"informative\"}}}}]},\"tabbedProductRive\":{\"title\":\"Prompt, code, and design from first idea to final product\",\"riveFile\":{\"alt\":\"A web development interface showing a music player design project. The main display features a dark music player for \\\"Dreamy Haze\\\" with a colorful spinning disc visualization and a playlist showing track details including BPM and duration. The left sidebar contains project notes about functionality.\",\"ratio\":1.9035,\"src\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/files/599r6htc/regionalized/b78441508d9a5200f5757e31b7cbc713a2e532fb.riv\",\"mobileSrc\":\"https://cdn.sanity.io/files/599r6htc/regionalized/29aadd65f4e5e3b51c6c653eed85f5f4b573164e.riv\",\"mobileRatio\":null},\"products\":[{\"_type\":\"homepageCosmosHeroProduct\",\"product\":\"prompt\",\"copy\":\"Prompt to code anything you can imagine with AI.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Explore Figma Make\",\"ariaLabel\":null,\"displayType\":\"link\",\"location\":\"carousel_figma_make\",\"behavior\":\"link\",\"target\":\"/make/\",\"openInNewTab\":false,\"advancedSettings\":null}},{\"_type\":\"homepageCosmosHeroProduct\",\"product\":\"design\",\"copy\":\"Design and refine products with your team, in one shared design file.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Explore Figma Design\",\"ariaLabel\":null,\"displayType\":\"link\",\"location\":\"explore_design\",\"behavior\":\"link\",\"target\":\"/design/\",\"openInNewTab\":null,\"advancedSettings\":null}},{\"_type\":\"homepageCosmosHeroProduct\",\"product\":\"draw\",\"copy\":\"Illustrate with vector editing, fills and effects, brushes, and more.\",\"cta\":{\"text\":\"Explore Figma Draw\",\"ariaLabel\":null,\"displayType\":\"link\",\"location\":\"explore_draw\",\"behavior\":\"link\",\"target\":\"/draw/\",\"openInNewTab\":null,\"advancedSettings\":null}},{\"_type\":\"homepageCosmosHeroProduct\",\"product\":\"build\",\"copy\":\"Give developers the details they need to build efficiently